		<title>英镑兑美元在零售销售数据公布前下跌</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hans/analysis/market-news/gbpusd-drops-ahead-of-retail-sales</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
